CSS Link Properties:

Links can also be styled by using CSS properties.


There are 4 states in a link & all the states can be formatted using CSS properties.

## a:link 		==>	 	unvisited link
## a:visited 	==>		visited link
## a:hover		==>		When a user moves the mouse pointer over it
## a:active		==>		The moment the user clicked on a link	


